brought together and I feel our power growing stronger with each minute.  The
next components my lord requests of me is that of a liquid form.  Seek the
protector of those who dwell among the water for our next reagents mortal.  Go
now.'  The voice quickly dissipates from within your head and you find yourself
again in reality.
