'Well done!' your head rumbles as the remenants of the elemental plane of water
are placed before Rozkadrath. 'Your powers amaze me mortal.  For such tasks to
be completed with such persistance you will surely rewarded beyond your wildest
dreams.'  For a second your thoughts are your own... dreams of riches, power,
