one could ever spend in their lifetime... then all is gone and the voice once
again controls your mind... 'The components of the elemental plane of water will
surely please his highness, however, the fires of the abyss do burn every so
brightly and its flames will not embrace these reagants warmly.  I require a
relic with regenerative powers which will preserve the inegrity of the delicate
reagants.  Seek for me the necklace of the one who sits on a throne of water.
Go now mortal.'
~
