Q
Rozkadrath laughs as you hand him the helmet of the demon prince Demogorgon
'Fool!  Did he think he could evade our forces forever?  Hah!'  Your head is
silent for a moment as the glabrezu examines the reagent.  Once again his
thundering voice fills your mind 'Young mortal, this brings great pleasure to
Joukarth, and I assure you the riches you shall receive are greater than you can
every conceive.  It has been a long road indeed, however we have come to the
requirement of the final ingredients.'  A soft chuckle can be heard by the demon
as he speaks his words in your mind 'You have proved to be quite strong indeed,
however, let us see how smart you are.  The final reagent my lord requires to
complete the incantation is that of the elemental plane of earth... but this
will require reagents of both a solid and crushed state.  I know it is alot to
ask for, but this shall be the last my lord requires of your services, and all
the power and riches promised by him shall be yours.  Go quickly mortal and
return to me the final reagents.'  The remenants of the voice still lingering,
you fade back into reality, the final task before you.
~
